onhashchange.doc:
Function to call when the fragment identifier part (starting with the hash (
<code>'#'</code>
) character) of the document's current address has changed.

width.doc:
The width of the video's display area, in
<a href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-values/#px" class="external" rel=" noopener">CSS pixels</a>
(absolute values only;
<a href="https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/embedded-content.html#dimension-attributes" class="external" rel=" noopener">no percentages</a>
).
